About this item

  • Smart Remote Control: The smart plug works with amazon alexa and google home which helps to manage your home devices through voice control. You can control home appliances remotely and smartly by your phone or tablet when you use Only tuya/smart life App.
  • Timer Function: Switch your home appliances on/off automatically and intelligently by setting a specific time with the smart plug. You can make a schedule for the air conditioner and pre-set your house lit before coming home.
  • Fantastic Design: Easy to install, no hub and subscription required; Super mini body and compact design, does not take up much space.
  • Energy Saving: With the convenient timer function, the smart plug can protect the devices safely and prevent your appliances from overcharging and overheating, and reducing energy use.
  • Easy to Install and Safe: Just plug a device into the smart wifi and alexa outlet and connect to your Wi-Fi network with tuya App. The mart plug uses high-quality materials and technology, such as V-0 flame-retardant thermoplastics, pure copper connectors and advanced PCBA boards. It can avoid fire hazards and provide overload protection to ensure the safety of family members.

Product Description

Description:
1. WiFi remote control and device state device icon. Device state always simultaneous display on APP
2. Share ControlShare the devices with other tuya accounts.
3. Timing: Support max 8 enabled single/repeat/countdown timing schedules each device.
4. Set default power on status default device status: ON or OFF when the device is power on.
5. Scene/Smart Scene: You can set up scenes or smart trigger on/off the device.

    How customer reviews and ratings work

    Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

    To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
